'''Tol-Kachorn''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Yinchorr/Legends|Yinchorr]]. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] discovered that [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] was on Yinchorr. The [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Marcellin Wessel]] held the [[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]] [[Council of Elders (Yinchorri)|Council of Elders]] hostage, in exchange for the council's release, the Yinchorri attempted to deliver Leia Organa captive to the Empire. In the end, the Empire slaughtered the council, and the Yinchorri rebelled. As a result, the [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]] devastated the [[Planet/Legends|world]], destroying Tol-Kachorn.<ref name="AA">''[[Alien Anthology]]''</ref>

